Name: MSI MAG A750BN PCIE5
Extra Notes/Information: A-BN with 300W 12VHPWR connection. Claims sleeve bearing; unknown quality fan. Does not claim ATX 3.0 compliance.

Name: MSI MAG A750GL PCIE5
Extra Notes/Information: Solid electrical performance; let down by poorly tuned protections; mediocre transient response; and a low quality fan.

Name: Vetroo 50315153244479
Extra Notes/Information: Advertised as ATX 3.1. Platform has poor transient response in 200% ATX 3.1 test; weak 3.3V load regulation; and high-set OCP on minor rails.

Name: Super Flower Leadex III Gold UP
Extra Notes/Information: Chinese caps; 20AWG gauges on the EPS/PCIe cables; 5VSB regulation doesn't quite hit A tier specifications.

Name: ASRock Phantom Gaming PG-750G
Extra Notes/Information: 12V-2x6 connector (GPU side) has thermistors to act as an "OTP" against melting. Stellar ripple suppression; especially on the minor rails.
